ji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T02:25:30.000Z","msg":"冇可能<br />\n第一：醫管局架構繁複，要改一條guideline要上，10萬個會，佢呢個時候一定改唔切<br />\n第二：感染控制有國際準則，唔係佢話要改就改。<br />\n所以醫管局俾唔到適當保障裝備員工，就一定係違規違法！我哋只要捉住佢呢一個痛腳，儲足夠嘅案例，到時可以集體訴訟集體，要求集體賠償。又或者將佢當作籌碼，迫使醫管局唔對罷工會員秋後算帳<br />\n所以總之醫管局一有違規即刻上報，將來一定可以發揮作用。"},{"pid":"8826ca0b7e37c84ccee76fe7c3953d237c120aed","tid":1875625,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26ddeabc33a7e901593b49a30b6f657a0146bfe","tid":1875625,"uid":29319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a0cdb07eb9d81ca3400db847a3bc78022a176eb","tid":1875625,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be72ffc6e2cba78d892d91ca2a46f209e6fc02ed","tid":1875625,"uid":52912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73896140794c8fe6f3d18a20e6c5cb091ac9f525","tid":1875625,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}